t: "S־µ mogyae mmaa no na wֽ»n (Idda) ber־µ no rey־µ aso, (na s־µ mosan p־µ wֽ»n a), monsֽ» wֽ»n mu ֽ»kwan pa so, (s־µ momp־µ wֽ»n so a), monyae wֽ»n wֽ» ay־µmy־µ mu; na (mo mmoa pa) nnye wֽ»n s־µ moreha wֽ»n na monnkֽ»to mmara. Obi a ֽ»b־µy־µ saa no nokor־µ s־µ wasisi ֽ»no ara ne ho. Na monhw־µ yie na moanfa Nyankopֽ»n ns־µm no anni f־µw, na monkae Nyankopֽ»n adom a ־µwֽ» mo so ne de־µ yasiane ama mo wֽ» Nwoma no mu ne Nyansa no a ֶ†de retu mofoֽ» no. Na monsuro Nyankopֽ»n na monhunu s־µ, Nyankopֽ»n ne biribiara ho Nimdefoֽ»"